page.title: 08BRYNFORD CLUBS
page.content: When I go to Brownies I pay my subs which are 15p. We have Brownie ring. Brownie ring is when you get together and sing a song. I am in the Gnomes six. We play games and sometimes we go on trips and picnics. We go from 5 till half-past 6. After Brownies I go to the shop for sweets. We wear a brown dress, a yellow tie, a brown belt and hat. Our guider wears a blue uniform. We call her Brown owl. { Thai boxing A local man who organises boxing in the area lives near Brynford.He has a gym.He has boxing gloves, punching bag and exercise machines. The different boxing he does is free-style boxing upper-cut and round out which is all part of Thai boxing.
